OL,3,CManchester Arena plotter refuses to
OL,4,Cappear in court on attempted murder
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FManchester Arena bomb plotter Hashem
OL,8,FAbedi has refused to appear in court,
OL,9,Fafter being charged with attempting to
OL,10,Fmurder prison officers at a maximum
OL,11,Fsecurity jail in County Durham.
OL,13,FThe 28-year-old did not appear on a
OL,14,Fscheduled videolink at Westminster
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday morning
OL,16,F(18 September), forcing an adjournment
OL,17,Fof the case.
