OL,3,CManchester Arena plotter refuses to
OL,4,Cappear in court on attempted murder
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FHe is accused of three counts of
OL,8,Fattempted murder, after four prison
OL,9,Fofficers were injured at HMP Frankland
OL,10,Fon 12 April 2025.
OL,12,FAbedi also faces one charge of assault
OL,13,Foccasioning actual bodily harm and one
OL,14,Fcount of unauthorised possession of a
OL,15,Fknife or offensive weapon.
OL,17,FThree prison officers were taken to
OL,18,Fhospital with serious injuries after
OL,19,Fthey were allegedly attacked with hot
OL,20,Foil and makeshift weapons in an ambush.
