OL,3,CManchester Arena plotter refuses to
OL,4,Cappear in court on attempted murder
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FAbedi is next due to appear at the
OL,8,Fsame court on 25 September.
OL,10,FChief Magistrate Paul Goldspring told
OL,11,Fthe court he would ensure the
OL,12,Fdefendant attends the next hearing,
OL,13,Fadding: "I will order that he is
OL,14,Fphysically produced, but if that is
OL,15,Fnot possible, it will be a prison
OL,16,Fvideolink."
