OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FAt the time of the incident, the
OL,8,FPrison Officers Association said the
OL,9,Fstaff sustained life-threatening
OL,10,Finjuries including burns, scalds and
OL,11,Fstab wounds in an "unprovoked" and
OL,12,F"vicious" attack.
OL,14,FAbedi was convicted of assisting with
OL,15,Fthe Manchester terror plot, in which
OL,16,Fhis brother, suicide bomber Salman
OL,17,FAbedi, killed 22 people by detonating
OL,18,Fa homemade rucksack-bomb in a crowd of
OL,19,Fconcert-goers.
